Wang said: 'When I saw the report about the goat, I felt I had the responsibility to protect it as it is so earnest for life.

'I want to bring it up as its strong spirit is the best drug to me'.

The goat was apparently born in a litter of four in August.

Farmer Zhao Jinfeng said: 'The mother goat produced litters before and they were all healthy and normal, but this one among four only has two hind legs.'

