According to Zhao, a month after its birth the two-legged goat started to teach itself how to walk on its hind legs.

A vet said the abnormality was due to genetic mutation.

Wang is the eldest of five children. In 2002, he was admitted by Anhui University, but two years later was forced to quit because his family was in so much poverty.

After working for two years, he returned the university and graduated in 2008. He now runs a start-up company with a friend.

